text: Heinz Wehrli (born 24 June 1953) is a Swiss equestrian. He competed in the team eventing at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Switzerland Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from the canton of Zürich
